flowchart TD
    U[User selects file] --> P[Storage signed upload to client-documents bucket]
    P --> R[INSERT client_documents row<br/>RLS: can_upload_client]
    R --> Q[Enqueue client_document_extraction_queue]
    Q --> CL[classify-document edge fn]
    CL --> EX[extract-document-data edge fn]
    EX --> ROW[INSERT client_document_extractions]
    ROW --> VF[Optional verify-document]
    VF --> DV[INSERT document_verifications]
    R --> FP[document_fingerprints duplicate check]
    R --> TL[client_timeline event_type=file]